Package: ggshadow
Title: Shadow and Glow Geoms for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Marc", "Menem", , "marc.menem@m4x.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of Geoms for R's 'ggplot2' library.
    geom_shadowpath(), geom_shadowline(), geom_shadowstep() and
    geom_shadowpoint() functions draw a shadow below lines to make busy
    plots more aesthetically pleasing. geom_glowpath(), geom_glowline(),
    geom_glowstep() and geom_glowpoint() add a neon glow around lines to
    get a steampunk style.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/marcmenem/ggshadow/
BugReports: https://github.com/marcmenem/ggshadow/issues
